data.description: This is your OPPORTUNITY to Own a 4 Bedroom 3.25 Bath, 2 Car Garage home on a PREMIER CORNER LOT with NO HOA!  Just over 1.5 Acres in the up and coming town of Haymarket.  NEWER Roof, Windows, HVAC, Water Heater, & some appliances (less than 5 yrs old).  This family owned home has been loved and cared for over the years and now you too can make it your own and create memories for years to come!  PEACE & SERENITY come to mind as you drive onto this PRIVATE LOT filled with mature trees and open spaces.  A lovely sprawling front yard precedes the home as it sits back from the street.  The long driveway will accommodate plenty of vehicles and the 2 Car Side Load garage will be sure to provide shelter for both you, your tools, and toys!  Once inside this larger Split Foyer home you'll find upstairs the main living area, to include a SPACIOUS Living Room with bay window, REMODELED Eat-In Kitchen with stainless appliances and Breakfast/Dining table space, Primary Bedroom with dual closet and Primary Bath.  Two Additional bedrooms are just a few steps away from another full bath down the hall.  The lower level is COZY and ready for relaxing or entertaining complete with a LARGE Rec Room, Propane Gas Fireplace, 4th Bedroom and another Full Bath with Jetted Soaking Tub!  The utility and laundry areas have ample space to move around and also there is a Quarter Bath (shower) that was designed to be handicap accessible (may not be to code).  To the rear of the home is a multi tier deck, storage shed, plenty of shade, and mother nature!  Don't miss the opportunity to own your piece of the pie!  The Haymarket area is rich with shops, restaurants, and museums. Some of the county's finest schools and reasonable tax rates make this area a great place to live and settle in.  Nearby commuter access, interstates, and HOV (Hot Lanes) make getting to and from surrounding cities or work hubs easy and convenient.
